            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>網飛(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:NFLX:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/NFLX\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">NFLX-US</a>)截至台北時間05日22:30股價下跌5.18美元，報98.04美元，跌幅5.02%，成交量11,849,368（股），盤中最高價98.75美元、最低價98.01美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：+0.09%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：+0.23%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：+0.38%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：+1.41%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>網飛(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:NFLX:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/NFLX\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">NFLX-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：-3.36%</li> <li>近 1 月：-90.49%</li> <li>近 3 月：-91.73%</li> <li>近 6 月：-91.61%</li> <li>今年以來：-88.28%</li></ul></section></main>",
